text: On Monday 5 February 2024, I had fried Hokkien prawn noodle for my lunch at The Marketplace @ 58 outlet in Bedok after walking from Tanah Merah MRT station on the East-West MRT line by using exit A and the hokkien prawn noodle tasted very delicious. Overall, the service provided to me was very good and it cost me $4.00. I would love to try these delightful carrot cake and fried Hokkien prawn noodle dishes from this branch in the future.
Enjoyed this hokkien mee. Usually order $4 portion enough for 1pax.
Hokkien Mee was one of the best I've eaten!
